node.text: Called out to fight, I humbled the little upstart. Today...was a good day.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Robert Whittaker on July 14, 2021 tagging @standstrongboxinggym, @sofiamareewhittaker, and @graciejiujitsusmeatongrange. May be an image of 4 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Isolation living. Making the most of it with the family but also looking forward to school starting up again 😅 Hope you guys are hanging in there 👊🏽
